---
title: Double Honey-Glazed Haloumi Caesar-Style Salad with Dijon Dressing & Almonds
description: You can put down that supermarket salad because we have one that will truly blow you away with sweetly glazed haloumi and toasted
almonds sprinkled on top. The croutons add a golden crunch while the dijon mayo dressing wraps everything up with a tasty bow.
